rComments: I took ECE 561 when she first offered it. Boring and dry, unclear in many instances, bad lecture scheduling and unprofessional insofar as canceling and rescheduling classes. At the time, she clearly did not enjoy teaching that much but I am sure she has improved. Knowledgeable and smart, but overall this was one of the most boring courses I took
She is similar to Prof. Hasegawa-Johnson. A little bit boring but very clear lectures. She is also very friendly.
She's a little boring, but pretty clear in her concepts. She is willing to talk outside of class and is pretty helpful
